title: Jean Lafitte National Historical Park and Preserve: Cooperating Association
body: Explore This Park    Get Involved     Support Your Park     Cooperating Association              Cooperating Association         Every Jean Lafitte site has a museum store with books, music, DVDs, and more chosen just for that site. For example, at the Chalmette Battlefield store, you can find items from history books to flags to reproduction cannons! AJ Sisco  Jean Lafitte's visitor center museum stores are managed by the Eastern National Parks Association, a not-for-profit organization that uses its proceeds to support America's national parks. Visit their website.
